585
00:23:22,440 --> 00:23:23,599
at dumating upang magdulot ng gulo araw-araw.

586
00:23:23,920 --> 00:23:25,160
Maya-maya lang, dumating si Xing Wu

587
00:23:25,160 --> 00:23:25,960
Naghahanap ng trabaho.
Walang imik,

588
00:23:26,960 --> 00:23:27,640
