663
00:26:00,440 --> 00:26:01,440
Paano ka namin hahayaang magbayad?

664
00:26:01,759 --> 00:26:02,680
-Pwede mo akong treat sa susunod.
-Ate.

665
00:26:03,559 --> 00:26:04,000
Oras na para umalis.

666
00:26:04,440 --> 00:26:05,279
Nandito si Quanya.
Aalis na ako.

667
00:26:06,079 --> 00:26:07,079
Tandaan mo ang ating kasunduan.

668
00:26:09,599 --> 00:26:10,400
Qing Ye, Wu.

669
00:26:10,720 --> 00:26:11,400
Aalis na kami.

670
00:26:11,440 --> 00:26:12,440
- Sige, paalam.
- Paalam.

671
00:26:14,759 --> 00:26:15,240
Pumunta.

672
00:26:16,559 --> 00:26:17,319
Anong kasunduan?

673
00:26:19,240 --> 00:26:19,920
Wala kang pakialam.

674
00:26:22,000 --> 00:26:22,920
Wala akong pakialam? / Wala akong pakialam?

675
00:26:24,200 --> 00:26:24,920
Teka, teka.

676
00:26:25,480 --> 00:26:26,920
Ano ba ang pinagbubulungan ninyong dalawa?

677
00:26:27,640 --> 00:26:28,599
Nakaka-curious talaga, 'no?

678
00:26:31,279 --> 00:26:31,680
Huh, sabihin mo na.

679
00:26:32,599 --> 00:26:33,759
Sabi ni Shu Han,

680
00:26:34,000 --> 00:26:36,039
May ipinakilala siyang bagong trabaho sa iyo.

681
00:26:36,440 --> 00:26:37,279
Kailangan mong pumunta sa Xinhai

682
00:26:37,279 --> 00:26:38,359
